#M ;; TRANSLITERATION SCHEME: NORMAN
#M [MONGOLKA] > U+183A ; MONGOLIAN LETTER KA ; Before a, o.
#M [SIBEGAA] > U+186C ; MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE GAA ; Before a, o.
#M [SIBEHAA] > U+186D ; MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE HAA ; Before a, o.
#M t s > U+186E ; MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE TSA ; Before a, e, o, u.
#M t s i > U+186E U+185F ; MONGOLIAN_LETTER_SIBE_TSA MONGOLIAN_LETTER_SIBE_IY; Before i.
#M d z > U+186F ; MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE ZA ;
#M [SIBERAA] > U+1870 ; MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE RAA ; Before a, e, o, u.
#M ; zcombcaron > U+1870 ; combined -> MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE RAA ; Before a, e, o, u.
#M ; Z > U+1870 ; MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE RAA ;
#M j y > U+1877 U+1873 ; MONGOLIAN_LETTER_MANCHU_ZHA MONGOLIAN LETTER MANCHU I ; Before i.
#M c y > U+1871 U+1873 ; MONGOLIAN LETTER SIBE CHA MONGOLIAN LETTER MANCHU I ; Before i.
