#M
#M ; PUNCTUATION
# M virgule > U+1808 ; MONGOLIAN MANCHU COMMA
# M fullstop > U+1809 ; MONGOLIAN MANCHU FULL STOP
# M hyph > U+202F U+200D ; NARROW NO-BREAK SPACE + ZERO WIDTH JOINER ; Perhaps we need to change this in a future version, as the Unicode specification uses only U+202F for case suffixes, but fonts will not display the correct form automatically, therefore we need to work around this by using U+200D to get the normal forms for suffixes, i. e. final forms.

